---
title: Garlic Herb Butter Shrimp & Lobster Tails with Lemony Asparagus & Chive Crème Fraîche Mashed Potatoes
description: Bring the white tablecloth vibes to your dinner table with this surf ’n’ surf dish. Lobster tails are basted with a rich garlic-herb butter, which is also used to top spiced shrimp. The crustacean celebration is paired with lemony roasted asparagus, plus an epic twist on mashed potatoes. Our secret? We blend in butter, chives, and a dollop of crème fraîche for ultimate silky goodness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/garlic-herb-butter-shrimp-lobster-tails-a1e71582.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/garlic-herb-butter-shrimp-lobster-tails-63cff8b42e534c666d088479-5cee240e.pdf
